                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180218-80-off417 t18180218-80-cd418"></join>, two spades, value 5s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18180218-80-victim513" type="victimName">
                     James 
